It is hard to overstate the versatility of a synthetic insulated shell like the Arcteryx Atom LT Jacket for men. Its lightweight, low bulk and breathable design offers easy care and all-weather warmth. You can wear this wind resistant jacket alone or layer up when the mercury really dips. The synthetic Coreloft insulation in the torso and arms offers great compressibility for easy packing, while the Polartec Power Stretch side panels with Hardface Technology enhance the jacket's breathability and promote unrestricted movement. You can throw this warm jacket on over a light layer or under your storm shell for the warmth you need in the alpine environment. Arcteryx keeps the Atom LT functional with stretch-knit cuffs and a durable water repellent finish. The Arcteryx Atom LT Jacket for men is your ticket to core warmth from summit to sidewalk.<div id=""shipping_info"">

You can count on the Arcteryx Men's Atom LT Hoody for lightweight, wind beating insulation. Weather resistant and breathable, this synthetic puffy jacket is a great standalone piece in fair weather or as a layering piece in cold, stormy conditions. The synthetic Coreloft insulation has a high warmth-to-weight ratio and is very compressible for easy packing. The Atom LT Hoody delivers all-weather warmth and easy-care versatility. The side panels and underarms use Polartec Power Stretch with Hardface Technology. These panels add increased breathability and enhance the jacket's ability to move with your body. Arcteryx includes stretch-knit cuffs keep to keep out the cold and insulates the hood for the ultimate in storm protection. Fire up your mountain stoke with the Arcteryx Men's Atom LT Hoody.<div id=""shipping_info"">

view larger       Warm, compressible and incredibly lightweight, the Transcendent Hoody is built to keep you comfortably insulated when the temperature drops, then stuff away into a corner of your pack when not needed. The hoody's high-quality 650 down fill insulation keeps you cozy during cross-country rambles or when you're huddled at camp, yet stows neatly for uphill slogs. For multi-day treks, it packs down so small you'll have a hard time not finding space to bring it along. Details Fit: Standard Fabric: 100% polyester, 20D ripstop outer

You can count on the Arcteryx Men's Atom LT Hoody for lightweight, wind beating insulation. Weather resistant and breathable, this synthetic puffy jacket is a great standalone piece in fair weather or as a layering piece in cold, stormy conditions. The synthetic Coreloft insulation has a high warmth-to-weight ratio and is very compressible for easy packing. The Atom LT Hoody delivers all-weather warmth and easy-care versatility. The side panels and underarms use Polartec Power Stretch with Hardface Technology. These panels add increased breathability and enhance the jacket's ability to move with your body. Arcteryx includes stretch-knit cuffs keep to keep out the cold and insulates the hood for the ultimate in storm protection. Fire up your mountain stoke with the Arcteryx Men's Atom LT Hoody.<div id=""shipping_info"">

Built for alpine versatility, the Fortrez Hoody is an alpine essential. The hoody takes full advantage of Polartec Power Stretch with Hardface Technology. The fabric is an exceptionally warm fleece with superior abrasion resistant properties. A smooth face that sheds moisture and layers easily and a high level of versatility makes it well suited to mixed alpine conditions. A trim, athletic fit keeps the Fortrez close to the body, which helps achieve better thermal efficiency and facilitates rapid transfer of moisture vapor. This also allows easy layering as conditions change. The hood is streamlined with the stretch in the fabric, allowing it to layer under a helmet or StormHood. A Phasic AR panel is integrated into the hood to be used as a neck gaiter or balaclava. Arc'teryx knows that ergonomic freedom is essential. Leveraging articulated patterning, underarm gussets and stretch materials, the Fortrez moves with the body. The longer cut and drop back hem stay put under a harness or hip belt. Flatlock construction minimizes seam irritation. The two hand pockets are streamlined, and a small pocket on the sleeve is easily accessible. Arc'teryx trim fitting garments share motion-friendly traits with the Athletic fit, but are patterned with lower volume for reduced bulk. The trim fit is sized for a base layer and a trim synthetic or down filled mid-layer. Polartec Power Stretch with Hardface Technology-88% polyester, 12% elastane, 230 g/m. A four-way stretch fabric that allows for excellent athletic movement and good breathability to maintain comfort. Some products feature Hardface Technology for a higher level of abrasion resistance.<div id=""shipping_info"">

ラットフィンクは1960年代のアメリカのティーンエージャーを中心に大人気と
なったキャラクターです。イラストレーターのエド・ロスが生み出した、このネズミの
キャラクターの誕生は1961年のクリスマスにレストランのナプキンに落書きした
のがはじまりと言われています。
